long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This SEO extension displays the most important SEO features of any given URL like title, meta, word count and meta keywords and more. It allows you to easily copy to clipboard each of the seo fields so that you can make changes to it and improve your seo performance. It also includes a quick link to open google page speed, google rich results test, similar web and gtmetrix.  It is lightweight and is a must have tool for all technical seo pros. 

Key Features:

1. Title
2. Meta Description
3. URL
4. Canonical URL.
5. Robots Tag.
6. X robots tag.
7. Meta Keywords.
8. Word count.
9. Google page speeds one click open.
10. Google rich results test one click open.
11. Similarweb one click open.
12. Gtmetrix one click open.
